                        http://www.csc.org.il/db/browse.aspx?db=SB&amp;sL=S&amp;sK=Segestan&amp;sT=keywords </idno>
                    <bibl xml:id="bib409-1">
                        <title xml:lang="syr">ܒܪ̈ܘܠܐ ܒܕܝܪ̈ܐ ܕܥܠ ܡܪܕܘܬ ܝܘܠܦܢ̈ܐ ܣܘܪ̈ܝܝܐ ܗܕܝܪ̈ܐ</title>
